[
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.1",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "But of the times and the seasons, brethren, ye have no need that I write unto you.",
    "hash": "e7b78c00493fc3e484f580b09462f570040509197307f6c2aa0c1120c29de1fc"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.2",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 2,
    "text": "For yourselves know perfectly that the day of the Lord so cometh as a thief in the night.",
    "hash": "ded0549d4a71f77313236e4c44ca296c61d992d488907c104c248cedcf2f4463"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.3",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 3,
    "text": "For when they shall say, Peace and safety; then sudden destruction cometh upon them, as travail upon a woman with child; and they shall not escape.",
    "hash": "f13fe7ef3b3c412520e71ebe62ec048bac086b8184507d4e4e7c6a76d3f7dc43"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.4",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 4,
    "text": "But ye, brethren, are not in darkness, that that day should overtake you as a thief.",
    "hash": "5dc183aa3699f9a650924dffcc634cd5741f761b010201c0ce14a4c43f4239f9"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.5",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 5,
    "text": "Ye are all the children of light, and the children of the day: we are not of the night, nor of darkness.",
    "hash": "1c867a4290b65a1d95c3807affe609781f7e449fcfe92f507fc046b7d5448fe2"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.6",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 6,
    "text": "Therefore let us not sleep, as {do} others; but let us watch and be sober.",
    "hash": "5fda39d8aad11535ef756ae2074e9b2e4fb8dc6c7114da686ead3fc07aeed5c8"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.7",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 7,
    "text": "For they that sleep sleep in the night; and they that be drunken are drunken in the night.",
    "hash": "a5ecd30a3de3bff364087d78e453a4a4cfd21c4c54cf541b8986ac51896838c3"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.8",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 8,
    "text": "But let us, who are of the day, be sober, putting on the breastplate of faith and love; and for an helmet, the hope of salvation.",
    "hash": "5470cdc84f8ee543ebb17156dcf18d819538fb7102f77cde530d904797e341e8"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.9",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 9,
    "text": "For God hath not appointed us to wrath, but to obtain salvation by our Lord Jesus Christ,",
    "hash": "31acad4ad9d55deff538f9f6d8ab71409ea4897a3b670f1f45f997ed0c3b193e"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.10",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 10,
    "text": "Who died for us, that, whether we wake or sleep, we should live together with him.",
    "hash": "e721823ff021de29390b747538de75383e10776ba9957bb2bdf7c911195a6ae5"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.11",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 11,
    "text": "Wherefore comfort yourselves together, and edify one another, even as also ye do. {comfort: or, exhort}",
    "hash": "c3f33da3596889668273a8d3e0254064dc2481d978b6dbe97bbebe432df86d30"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.12",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 12,
    "text": "And we beseech you, brethren, to know them which labour among you, and are over you in the Lord, and admonish you;",
    "hash": "17a3a332043370a508adda604b42e39facef877eae34ab09a0c0dd5396a468c6"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.13",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 13,
    "text": "And to esteem them very highly in love for their work's sake. {And} be at peace among yourselves.",
    "hash": "e542b22db1a93a21fc32acf4f00ead590c7ef82c45f7df4d0921dcf605e3b3f9"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.14",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 14,
    "text": "Now we exhort you, brethren, warn them that are unruly, comfort the feebleminded, support the weak, be patient toward all {men}. {exhort: or, beseech} {unruly: or, disorderly}",
    "hash": "e14848b98c95bf31ddd8eb7eec99d7df3cb0363fd906e0214b474518d01b04b3"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.15",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 15,
    "text": "See that none render evil for evil unto any {man}; but ever follow that which is good, both among yourselves, and to all {men}.",
    "hash": "437267d3824c4afceabc857eae136f34ba264db422cd93792fb09034a64880a6"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.16",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 16,
    "text": "Rejoice evermore.",
    "hash": "173697b08101f39032d8db3c32009cabe4a52ec72e00c5812da360911838b717"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.17",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 17,
    "text": "Pray without ceasing.",
    "hash": "2915c78170adf0e109c581cb562e1cbf6703e3dae2f91d2642768b7251774e7e"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.18",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "In every thing give thanks: for this is the will of God in Christ Jesus concerning you.",
    "hash": "31b648d2a18ad640347cc61267075a5fc945334d106da53eaed29013c7eca8a3"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.19",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 19,
    "text": "Quench not the Spirit.",
    "hash": "54394e27eb43107b87bacb9e731c3cf7293328f902ae8ab7bd0d86e04821cff8"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.20",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 20,
    "text": "Despise not prophesyings.",
    "hash": "97fd4733a4ab95028a536e97be26495a64ff8dcbc0f30ea8da7dda3af1e9e497"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.21",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 21,
    "text": "Prove all things; hold fast that which is good.",
    "hash": "7ba85b079b91c3707f1e75a1ca68d7557f90d92188058a752e17703ec4ec9caa"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.22",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 22,
    "text": "Abstain from all appearance of evil.",
    "hash": "7a97a44b998b5561a262da3fe62be302d684530b1bf1f88db72a6bff688c977c"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.23",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 23,
    "text": "And the very God of peace sanctify you wholly; and {I pray God} your whole spirit and soul and body be preserved blameless unto the coming of our Lord Jesus Christ.",
    "hash": "4eea9bca6e399affcf99c703e2bae6ce69da0aa13194ec2feb07e852cd992873"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.24",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 24,
    "text": "Faithful {is} he that calleth you, who also will do {it}.",
    "hash": "fa53eb97cc076588aa3955a4b58fd9ea7771553c4d06d6da219deb18f9a571b0"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.25",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 25,
    "text": "Brethren, pray for us.",
    "hash": "1b58e76bda4228e81bec976f9d37cb99865a52d5f665aa9c9d53ba8ec1b0e4ba"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.26",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 26,
    "text": "Greet all the brethren with an holy kiss.",
    "hash": "837178994ae52754ec0fa2aa55d286b5603cc99e00ba507e41198bf5275d341f"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.27",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 27,
    "text": "I charge you by the Lord that this epistle be read unto all the holy brethren. {charge: or, adjure}",
    "hash": "ab7bc9d427e86422d5feb7b02539e16f1170e4377d3b08cd7d273dfdf0d3c2e0"
  },
  {
    "id": "1TH.5.28",
    "book": "1 Thessalonians",
    "bookNum": 52,
    "bookAbbrev": "1TH",
    "chapter": 5,
    "verse": 28,
    "text": "The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ {be} with you. Amen. «{The first epistle} to the Thessalonians was written from Athens.»",
    "hash": "397ab37ca88911bcc7b50399f193926477e14fa737249bee3993fface02d77c0"
  }
]